channel.title: Fraps problem
channel.description:
I just Got the new version of Fraps so I decided to test it out. I recorded the video but when to see it it wasn't there and the thing is Fraps knows it recorded it because I opened the Fraps log and this was in it:
2010-01-30 08:17:00 - Psychonauts Frames: 1466 - Time: 23731ms - Avg: 61.776 - Min: 36 - Max: 77
So does anyone know how to fix this?
